data.description: Motivated Seller - Time to move on....Well kept and conveniently located townhome in Crestview's best townhome community!  Features include 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths with wood-grain tile throughout the ground floor living and common areas - galley kitchen with 1 year old dishwasher - ample living room with dining area - laundry/half bath combination on the ground floor for convenience - 3 roomy bedrooms on the 2nd floor for privacy - one car garage - back patio with greenspace and community pool views.  AC unit replaced in 2022 and new garage door opener in 2023.  Don't miss out on this end unit townhome in sought after Eagle's Landing conveniently located in Crestview's south end!
